description:
An Ordinals Collection by TAROrdinals.

Original 1:1 vector art inspired by the Tarot.
Holding an Eternal tarot image in your wallet, is like planting a seed that will grow into a fruitbearing tree.

This Tarot deck is a common good. Published under CC0 it's meant to be (de)evolved by generations to come.
name: The Eternal Tarot
